  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Everolimus in Reducing Total Native Kidney Volume in Polycystic Kidney Disease Transplanted Recipients</brief_title>
  <acronym>EVERKYSTE</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open-labelled Multicenter Randomized Study on the Efficacy of Everolimus in Reducing Total Native Kidney Volume in Kidney Transplanted Patients With Autosomal Dominant Polycystic Kidney Disease</official_title>
