  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age between 18 and 75 years-old

          -  recipients of a first kidney graft between 6 month and 5 years ago with a stable eGFR
             above 30 ml/min/1,73m2

          -  contraception for female recipients to avoid pregnancy

          -  valid health Insurance during the study period

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  signed informed consent not obtained
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
